response.overview: Victor is a powerful business man and associate of Lex L. Victor's sights have been set on the "man of steel" for years, but he's never had the ability to stop him. "Steel's" younger attractive cousin on the other hand, is a prime target. Victor has spent years analyzing her weaknesses, and after obtaining a store of kryptonium, he plans and constructs the perfect scenario to not only beat her, but to fully bring her over to the dark side, at least that's his intention. Her strength is not what it should be and she struggles to break his hold. Little does she know that the floor is infused with kryptonium. Victor attacks relentlessly and it becomes clear very quickly that our heroine is at a disadvantage. Between using krypto rocks, a collar, the krypto floor, and a compliance injection developed by Lex's lab, our heroine has no idea why she's not able to defend herself. See how far he takes our heroine. Will she survive as he tries to break her?
response.title: Dissension
